{"tid":294222,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"識得欣賞籃球，你係唔會亦唔應該捧勇士既。","createTime":"2017-06-22T18:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T23:49:58.000Z","uid":27416,"like":53,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19a789d8e331e1275cf0cbd98ae3ec2cc99b7c92","tid":294222,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:32:13.000Z","msg":"個人來說，我一直以來最憎的就是勇士。 <br />\n<br />\n他是唯一令我聯想到機械人踢打波的球隊。 <br />\n<br />\n從他們最擅長射罰球就可窺探一二。只有像訓練軍人一樣，抹殺人類情緒，才可確保罰球穩定的表現。 <br />\n<br />\n至於甚麼走位最機動，戰術最規律等等，說穿了就是把個人的想像、發揮，壓到最低。再把所謂團隊精神無限推高，高層在背後作充滿計算的數據分析，然後下達嚴格指令，球員聽命執行。 <br />\n<br />\n所以他們出色的球員，只有指揮型精神領袖，沒有藝術家一般的球星。curry算是一個異類，不過已經唔係隊中大佬。 <br />\n<br />\n而現今籃球愈來愈不可觀，就是因為這種意識已成主導。 <br />\n<br />\n當籃球愈發容不下個人的自發演繹，當kd的「穩定」正式超越lbj的「隨機」，籃球已死。 <br />\n<br />\n除下頭盔，準備中箭，讓我說句，識得欣賞籃球，你係唔會亦唔應該捧勇士既。"},{"pid":"331bf24c47049eaead938a7c8f99db6e36659e08","tid":294222,"uid":93964,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:33:35.000Z","msg":"膠 <br />\n人地改變局面 你就話唔應該捧"},{"pid":"1d1851b88df8ece7777d2d9d3987a9b9ef8fff01","tid":294222,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:34:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>膠 <br />\n人地改變局面 你就話唔應該捧</blockquote><br />\n一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9cb15e170b1663bb40f1d64190c5e965a25307","tid":294222,"uid":59989,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:34:25.000Z","msg":"假膠？似讚緊我勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a0316e226ae8914646c7b7ba09ef23e7bffdf7","tid":294222,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:34:31.000Z","msg":"(玩具版)今天勇士殺死了籃球"},{"pid":"4d46ff20d6e4741ebc0f37278ff8927fd5d9cfcf","tid":294222,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>膠 <br />\n人地改變局面 你就話唔應該捧</blockquote><br />\n一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nkd黎到拎得一個冠軍就話改變局面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2010fa23a0e1137b3a3e9692b3d04155f94dafa9","tid":294222,"uid":88943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:39:10.000Z","msg":"應該睇騎士，戰術只係高位pick and roll. 幾有戰術。"},{"pid":"71e7e4cc8915a19a604b794aea9c3aabb17352c8","tid":294222,"uid":52323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>膠 <br />\n人地改變局面 你就話唔應該捧</blockquote><br />\n一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nkd黎到拎得一個冠軍就話改變局面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家第一年你教我點拎2個冠軍"},{"pid":"e89255212cbb7f136a0d5409e324968c227819d0","tid":294222,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:45:45.000Z","msg":"好撚多真心"},{"pid":"a110fc872d0408ed281dc110786be95e4eaeeebb","tid":294222,"uid":107990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T22:16:00.000Z","msg":"曲到直 btw腐皮！"},{"pid":"092a4160571f690784f6cab4fedb0db51ee124ed","tid":294222,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T23:02:59.000Z","msg":"原文係德國足球潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2be106aa9c940d3ea4c268ccecd78b5c156fc9a","tid":294222,"uid":23706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T23:04:02.000Z","msg":"新會然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8930d366f26974cca5389e42f71f4e72ae9c5dac","tid":294222,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T23:31:13.000Z","msg":"On9 la 你有無睇今年既勇士ga?我吾覺有咩問題lor"},{"pid":"6f0b0ec1